Gematria
========

wxPython Application to calculate Gematria values. <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gematria>

Run Gematria with `python app.py` or build a Mac native application with `python setup.py py2app`

Features
--------

Gematria uses a sqlite database of words (words.db) and their corresponding
Gematria values. Users can add words, delete words, search for words to get their values, or search for values to find all words with a given value.
